svg.source: Title: Create Secret Santa Gift Exchange Event User-->User Interface: Click Create button User Interface-->User: Display Exchange Page User-->User Interface: Enters Data and Submit User Interface-->User Interface: Validates Data Note right of User Interface: If error, display message User Interface-->Server API: Calls create event API Server API-->Server API: Validates Data Note right of Server API: If error, return with error Server API-->Database: Save new event Database-->Server API: Saved event Server API-->User Interface: Saved event json User Interface-->User Interface: Show success message User Interface-->User: Redirect to list of events page
